{"tid":1156240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【騰訊養三代】騰訊上市時阿爸買入 小股東繼承後唔使返工 攜兒子出席股東會","createTime":"2019-05-15T13:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T13:40:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"57a062efe619b0b40ed518fd37d754a3972cfa51","tid":1156240,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190515/large/1557920899_aaa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190515%2Flarge%2F1557920899_aaa5.png&h=17975a66&s={SIZE}\" />「騰訊養三代」的李先生攜兒子出席股東會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190515/large/1557916668_5305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190515%2Flarge%2F1557916668_5305.jpg&h=1cdfb8f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小股東梁先生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190515/large/1557916675_d82c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190515%2Flarge%2F1557916675_d82c.jpg&h=3a931224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小股東黎先生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190515/large/1557916590_12cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190515%2Flarge%2F1557916590_12cf.jpg&h=ce582430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n騰訊今日舉行股東會兼發佈季績。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊（700）今日舉行股東會兼發佈季績，不少出席的股東都是騰訊的長情股東，有些持股更是由上一代傳給下一代。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【騰訊股東會】主婦股東投訴：點解個仔9點仲打到機？騰訊：係唔係騙案？<br />\n<br />\n李先生拖著幾歲的兒子一起出席股東會，他笑言手上騰訊股份是由爸爸於騰訊上市時買下，留下給他，「所以依家唔使返工！」但他拒絕透露持股數量，「秘密呀，驚被稅局搵我哋。」<br />\n<br />\n騰訊2004年上市，上市價為3.7元，計及股份1拆5因素，現時升幅近500倍，以當年一手成本3,700元計，現時價值為185萬元。<br />\n<br />\n另一股東黎先生持有約1000股騰訊，他稱自己都唔係持有好多，「都係少少啫。」他透露，目前為止都有得賺，但派息一向都不滿意，只希望股價向上，升至400元便會沽貨，「目前為止都有得執吓啦，（會唔會持貨至450元？）唔好啦，都唔好制啦，因為佢南非嗰間已經係410元，我諗（升勢）應該差唔多盡架啦。」南非企業Naspers為騰訊的大股東，在三月底計劃配售逾1.89億股騰訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁先生指，炒股票唔係談情，賺到就走。他自言至今都己沽貨數次，目前未有再沽貨的時間表，因他預期今年內股價會不會上升至400元，所以都會先持有，「賺到就走，但我諗今年都唔得架啦，個走勢都唔係咁強。」他對騰訊派息太少表不滿，指其他高息股都會有近六厘息，但騰訊三厘都沒有，「有時股價唔好的時候，你想話持有收息都唔得。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：劉曉鳴<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190515/59604275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190515%2F59604275&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2D632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=29d4c23f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190515%2F59604275&h=8c182cab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190515/59604275</a>"},{"pid":"5dee404f1855094c8fe955f7fd538d06db2cd04f","tid":1156240,"uid":98386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪父幹囉 成日講知足常樂班窮撚好心學下啦 自己冇本事要生又留唔到乜俾後人算啦 但唔好仲串串貢"},{"pid":"5a5c90957322307835a3e048fbaa0e1696e24c0e","tid":1156240,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"你一日唔放d錢都唔係你既"},{"pid":"9631c21413e5994d45ac630c5b29e08743ebe815","tid":1156240,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5a5c90957322307835a3e048fbaa0e1696e24c0e","tid":1156240,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"你一日唔放d錢都唔係你既"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"每個月平均袋幾萬現金股息"},{"pid":"c9449f7802f53ae1c09c573564794e4e9c661412","tid":1156240,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9631c21413e5994d45ac630c5b29e08743ebe815","tid":1156240,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5a5c90957322307835a3e048fbaa0e1696e24c0e","tid":1156240,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"你一日唔放d錢都唔係你既"},"citedBy":2,"reply